data.description:
This home wont last at this price reduction!  Motivated Seller! After 25 years of ownership, this beautiful Florida Shores home is ready for new owners!  Escape to your own private oasis with this charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom concrete block home(Roof 2019/AC 2021). As you step inside, you'll be greeted by the spacious open floor plan, highlighted by a stunning floor-to-ceiling fireplace that adds a touch of elegance to the living space. The 1867 sq ft layout provides ample room for comfortable living and entertaining, while large windows let in abundant natural light, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere throughout the home. Inside, discover a thoughtfully laid out split floor plan with generously sized bedrooms, and a spacious kitchen offering ample cabinet storage. The adjacent dining area offers a lovely space for enjoying meals together or hosting dinner parties. Step outside to discover your own private paradise. The screened in enclosure that surrounds the sparkling pool provides an ideal setting for outdoor relaxation and enjoyment. Whether you're lounging poolside or hosting a BBQ with loved ones, this area is sure to be a favorite gathering spot.
In addition to the main driveway, the property features an additional parking space designed to accommodate an RV or boat, ensuring that you have plenty of room for all your recreational vehicles.
Centrally located in Florida Shores, this home offers easy access to local amenities and is in close proximity to schools, dining, and entertainment options. Don't miss the chance to make this remarkable property your ownschedule a showing today and envision the endless possibilities of calling this house your home.
